Gun Digest Presents - Shooter's Guide 2014  USA

84 Pages | True PDF | English | 18 MB 


Gun Digest is proud to bring you its Shooter's Guide 2014, profiling the newest guns, gear, optics and ammunition on the market. The special edition is filled with informative profiles of the newest guns for 2014 and everything you'll need to deck them out. The issue is brimming with full-color photos of revolvers, pistols, bolt-action rifles, AR-15 and every type of shotgun imaginable. We're certain you'll find this a useful resource you'll turn back to again and again.
